Module count
Package count.gui.kit

Class CountActions

java.lang.Object
count.gui.kit.CountActions
public class CountActions
extends Object
Count actions:
  • Session
    1. load session (load XML)
    3. +load session by URL
    4. start new session (load tree)
    5. start new session
    6. add tree
    8. edit tree
    9. + close session
    10. save everything
  • Data
    1. open table, keep annotations
    2. open table, ignore annotations
    3. + open table, add star tree
    4. simulate data
    5. extract filtered
    6. convert to binary
  • Rates
    1. load rates
    2. optimize rates
  • Analysis
    1. Dollo
    2. numerical parsimony
    3. posteriors
